title: Legendary and Mythological Art (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Legendary and Mythological Art
Bracken Books | 1994 | ISBN: 1858911354 | English | 530 pages | PDF | 54.5 MB

Clara Erskine Clement's superbly illustrated handbook, describes and explains some of the world's greatest literary, religious and historical themes as depicted in painting and sculpture. Specific characters are identified through a detailed exploration of their attributes and the contexts in which they appear. Additionally, legends relating to particular towns and places are discussed
